03:50.780 --> 03:52.740
Well, I heard you.

03:53.260 --> 03:55.660
But you don't mean no.

03:58.820 --> 04:00.740
What's wrong?

04:01.700 --> 04:02.940
Nothing.

04:05.580 --> 04:07.380
