05:13.220 --> 05:15.540
The Voltes have
always had golden retrievers.

05:15.580 --> 05:17.660
They're very happy with them.

05:21.100 --> 05:23.620
There's an Irish Lab that I read about.

05:23.660 --> 05:27.300
