What do you think?

05:52.820 --> 05:55.860
Don't let me do this.
Don't let me do this, please.

05:55.900 --> 05:58.260
I don't want to start again.

05:58.700 --> 06:03.020
You promised, Earl.
You promised. Please. Please.

06:03.260 --> 06:06.580
Why do you fight it so hard, Earl?

06:25.340 --> 06:27.820
I'm going to stay up awhile,

06:28.220 --> 06:31.620
