16:05.220 --> 16:07.980
Hello, my name is Vaughn.

16:08.500 --> 16:10.620
I'm an alcoholic

16:10.660 --> 16:13.380
and I haven't had a drink in 10 months.

16:20.780 --> 16:22.500
Hi. My name's Earl

16:22.540 --> 16:24.140
and I'm an addict.

16:31.660 --> 16:34.740
- Anyone else?
- You are such a fucking hypocrite.

16:34.780 --> 16:36.780
If you were honest
you'd step up there and say,

16:36.820 --> 16:39.460
"Hi, I'm Earl. I killed two people last night.

16:39.500 --> 16:43.700
