17:35.340 --> 17:39.220
If not, we would love to work with you
further on the design.

17:39.260 --> 17:42.180
It's always fun to challenge our machines.

17:42.220 --> 17:44.220
Now, if you gentlemen would excuse me,

17:44.260 --> 17:47.540
