You're talking about emotion.

20:17.260 --> 20:18.780
Now, get up.

20:18.820 --> 20:22.500
In fact, your mother and I came this close
to selling out last year.

20:22.540 --> 20:23.620
- What?
- That's right.

20:23.660 --> 20:25.340
And had we been offered
a little more money,

20:25.380 --> 20:28.780
and they still may come back to us,
we would sell.

20:29.340 --> 20:30.900
What would you do without the business?

20:33.340 --> 20:34.740
